… Says Move Will Ensure Equity, Justice, Peace, Unity Of Nigeria The Indomitable Tinubu Support Organisation (ITSO) has commended President Muhammadu Buhari and the Northern governors of the All Progressives Congress (APC) for keeping fidelity to power balancing by endorsing the Southern Presidency in 2023 after the eight-year rule of a northern president. In a statement signed by the Director-General of ITSO, Abdoulbaq Ladi Balogun, the group hailed the decision of the northern governors, calling them true democrats and lovers of a united Nigeria. -Advertisement- It described the President as a unifier and hero of modern Nigeria where equity and justice prevail. Balogun further stated that this courageous and uncommon decision by the Northern APC governors will ensure equity, justice, peace and unity of the country, noting that history and posterity will remember them for good. “We commend this uncommon and unselfish patriotic stance by the Northern governors, supported by President Buhari that power should shift to the Southern part of the country. This is indeed a testimony to all Nigerians that indeed the best democrats and lovers of one Nigeria are in the APC; no wonder Nigerians have been voting en-masse for candidates of the party and we are convinced that with this stance, the APC will again be voted for at all levels of elections come 2023 by Nigerians”. The group commended the Jigawa State Governor, Alhaji Abubakar Badaru, for withdrawing from the race immediately and enjoining all other northern aspirants to respect the President and the Northern governors’ stance on fielding a southern candidate by stepping down their aspirations in order to ensure a rancour-free and peaceful convention. While urging all Southern presidential aspirants to close rank, be united and ensure a rancour-free convention; the statement appeal to delegates to ensure the emergence of a strong, experienced and formidable candidate, like Asiwaju Bola Ahmed Tinubu, who commands cult-like followership, just like President Buhari across the country, that will guarantee victory for the APC and ensure the continuation of the infrastructural transformation like the rail revolution, airport remodelling and construction, network of roads across the country and improvement in security.